6x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-spinning-bug-ban-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-spinning-bug-ban-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-2"><em>《反恐精英 2》</em></a>玩家表示，游戏将禁止那些在热身中旋转过快的玩家，而粉丝们对此不以为然。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-upcoming-games-we-saw-at-gamescom-2023-3505950"><strong>以下是我们在 Gamescom 2023 上看到的一些即将推出的最佳游戏</strong></a></li></ul><p>与发行服务上的大量其他游戏一样， <em>《反恐精英 2》</em>受<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>的 VAC Live 系统的约束——“VAC”代表“Valve Anti-Cheat”。</p><p>在线竞技游戏中的作弊行为不断演变，因此开发者必须对非法玩家试图规避其反作弊系统的最新策略做出反应。 </p><figure id="attachment_3418926" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3418926" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3418926" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes.jpg" alt="《反恐精英 2》。图片来源：Valve。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Counter-Strike-2-Dust-2-Smokes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3418926" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》图片来源：Valve。</figcaption></figure><p>然而， <em>《反恐精英 2》</em>的反作弊系统有时过于热情，错误地标记了那些<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-will-be-reversing-accidental-amd-bans-3519780">使用 AMD Anti-Lag+ 功能的用户。</a>现在，它影响了鼠标旋转过快的玩家。</p><p>两名 YouTube 用户通过<a href="https://www.pcgamesn.com/counter-strike-2/dpi-bug" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>PCGamesN</em></a>解释说，将鼠标的每英寸点数灵敏度设置为 10,000 以上，然后在热身部分旋转鼠标将导致禁止。</p><p> “这可能是 [ <em>Counter-Strike 2</em> ] 中最严重的错误，”另一位 X 用户 Jigglypuff64942 在<a href="https://twitter.com/Jigglypuff64942/status/1716086911255941543">一系列帖子中说道，这些帖子显示他们在不到一分钟的时间内就因为同样的事情而被封禁</a>。</p><p> Valve 的 VAC Live 系统可能认为这是“旋转机器人”。由于破坏性行为，作弊者利用这一点同时充当更难击中的目标，并且瞄准黑客将立即捕捉并射击进入玩家射程的任何目标。 </p><figure id="attachment_3519792" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3519792" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3519792" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/counter-strike-2-reinstating-AMD-bans-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3519792" class="wp-caption-text"> 《反恐精英 2》来源：Valve</figcaption></figure><p>尽管如此，如果玩家不知道并且更喜欢使用高每英寸点数的灵敏度设置进行游戏，这可能会导致他们被禁止参加<em>《反恐精英 2》</em> ，但实际上他们并不是一个坏演员。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/devolver-digital">Devolver Digital</a>透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hotline-miami-1-and-2-players-get-ps5-and-xbox-series-xs-upgrade-for-free-3520236">了 PS5 和 Xbox Series X|S 版<em>《迈阿密热线</em>》和<em>《迈阿密热线 2：错误号码》</em>的发布</a>，并为已经拥有这些游戏的用户提供免费升级。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2s-most-serious-bug-is-spinning-too-fast-say-fans-3520388">粉丝们表示，《反恐精英 2》的“最严重的错误”转得太快了，粉丝们</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
前 PlayStation 老板认为收购可能会导致游戏创意下降https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/former-playstation-boss-argues-acquisitions-could-lead-to-less-creative-games-3520256?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=former-playstation-老板认为收购可能会导致游戏创意减少Imogen DonovanTue, 24 Oct 2023 11:56:29 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3520256 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “时间会证明一切，但这有点令人担忧”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/former-playstation-boss-argues-acquisitions-could-lead-to-less-creative-games-3520256">前 PlayStation 老板认为收购可能会导致游戏创意减少，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-major-character-deaths-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony-interactive-entertainment">索尼互动娱乐</a>美国公司总裁兼首席执行官肖恩·雷登 (Shawn Layden) 表达了他对游戏行业整合对创造力影响的担忧。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/alan-wake-2-soundtrack-interview-sam-lake-fried-music-3510619">《心灵杀手 2》的“怪人流行歌曲”的制作过程</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://twitter.com/LANPartiesPod?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1714690087618048040%7Ctwgr%5E37039a7266c72fd468cd77bc7012db39d990a6fa%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fkotaku.com%2Fembed%2Finset%2Fiframe%3Fid%3Dtwitter-1714690087618048040autosize%3D1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LAN Party 播客</a>采访时，雷登同意收购能够为那些因开发成本而面临巨额账单的小型工作室提供生命线。</p><p>尽管如此，他说，正是这些小型工作室的存在表明了鼓励各种想法和可能性的环境。 </p><figure id="attachment_3507822" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3507822" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3507822" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023.jpg" alt="《使命召唤：现代战争 3》。图片来源：动视暴雪。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Call-Of-Duty-Modern-Warfare-3-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3507822" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》。图片来源：动视暴雪。</figcaption></figure><p> “我对整合的担忧是它常常会影响创造力。例如，它需要某种小型的、独立的、野马工作室，并将它们带入一个更大的集团，本质上，你越大，时间就越慢，”Layden（来自<a href="https://kotaku.com/sony-playstation-ps5-acquisition-preservation-1850951069?utm_source=vip" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Kotaku</em></a> ）解释道。</p><p> “我还担心，当工作室被收购时，他们可能会被吸收到一个正在制作更大游戏的更大的企业中，而不是提供一种创建游戏的方式，你知道，有多少工作室参与制作重磅游戏，这些游戏将会令人震惊思想。”</p><p>即使不包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/microsoft-now-officially-owns-call-of-duty-and-world-of-warcraft-after-acquisition-wraps-up-3514809">微软收购动视暴雪</a>，2023年该行业也将发生重大转变。今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/embracer-group">Embracer Group</a>宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/embracer-group-restructuring-brings-layoffs-studio-closures-and-game-cancellations-3455237">重组意向，这将导致其旗下的公司关闭</a>。</p><p>其中之一是<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/deep-silver-volition">Volition</a> ，该网站在其社交媒体渠道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/saints-row-developer-volition-shuts-down-only-two-months-after-its-30th-anniversary-3492123">庆祝成立 30 周年仅两个月后就被关闭</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3520384" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3520384" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3520384" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/saints-row-reboot-volition-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3520384" class="wp-caption-text"> 《黑道圣徒》图片来源：深银</figcaption></figure><p>自今年年初以来，全球范围内该行业已有大约 6,000 个职位流失， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/uk-games-industry-layoffs-continue-with-f1-manager-developer-frontier-3516571">Frontier</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-wolf-among-us-2-studio-allegedly-made-most-of-its-employees-redundant-3510684">Telltale Games</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-developer-is-the-latest-studio-to-be-hit-with-layoffs-3508507">Naughty Dog</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/team17-to-reportedly-make-tens-of-redundancies-this-month-3507780">Team17</a>等开发商都在应对裁员问题。</p><p> “我只是关心这会对工作室内部的创造力产生什么影响，他们能否保持这种独立的创造力，还是只是被更大的整体所吸收？”雷登总结了收购的潜在影响。</p><p> “时间会证明一切，但这有点令人担忧。当你从数百种声音变成数十种声音时，你会失去一些声音。”</p><p>如今，雷登是腾讯控股子公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/tencent">腾讯</a>游戏的战略顾问，腾讯控股是视频游戏行业投资规模最大的公司。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-xiv"><em>《最终幻想 14》</em></a>制作人兼导演吉田直树<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/final-fantasy-14-director-shares-dream-crossover-with-diablo-3519795">分享了他对<em>《暗黑</em>破坏神》联动版的渴望</a>——“如果我们能让它成功，我会非常高兴”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/former-playstation-boss-argues-acquisitions-could-lead-to-less-creative-games-3520256">前 PlayStation 老板认为收购可能会导致游戏创意减少，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
