2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3520252" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hotline-miami-on-ps5-and-xsx-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3520252" class="wp-caption-text"> “迈阿密热线”图片来源：Devolver Digital</figcaption></figure><p>他们根据速度、变化和鲁莽等方面进行评分，高分会奖励新武器和面具。</p><p>这款经典射击游戏被认为是有史以来最伟大的游戏之一，其续作通过设定在主角 Jacket 旅程之前、期间和之后的场景，充实了原作的事件<em>。</em></p><p>但是，评论家对第二款游戏的评价却大相径庭，尽管几乎所有人都认为配乐与原作相当。</p><p>第三款游戏并未列入 Dennaton Games 的议程，因为它以<em>《迈阿密热线 2：错误号码》</em>作为故事的结局。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，一位<em>《异形：隔离》</em>模组制作者将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/alien-isolation-modder-replaces-xenomorph-with-thomas-the-tank-engine-for-halloween-3519866">异形变成了托马斯坦克引擎</a>，为万圣节带来了季节性的恐慌。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hotline-miami-1-and-2-players-get-ps5-and-xbox-series-xs-upgrade-for-free-3520236">《迈阿密热线 1》和《迈阿密热线 2》玩家可免费获得 PS5 和 Xbox Series X|S 升级的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
